Package edu.utah.bmi.ibiomes.local.chem.gromacs

Manage local files and directories that represent experiments with the GROMACS software package.

    GROMACSParameterInputFile
    GROMACS parameter input file (.mdp) Defines the parameters for running the simulation, including time step, type of simulation, electrostatics, van der Waals, temperature coupling, pressure coupling, etc.
